# SecurePi — LOBBY preset:  python securePi.py @lobby.args
# presets/common.args is applied automatically as the base; this file only
# overrides what differs for this location.

# Busy public area: alert fast, and people pass close to bags all the time,
# so keep the owner radius tight.
--unattended-time 60
--proximity 120
--snapshot-dir alerts/lobby
